---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Zelipt"
	description="Zelipt is an AEO/GEO agency helping brands earn AI citations in ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity and Google AI Overviews."
>
	<section class="relative">
		<div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center">
			<div class="space-y-6 lg:col-span-7">
				<p
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-700"
				>
					<span aria-hidden="true" class="size-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-indigo-500 to-fuchsia-500"></span>
					AEO / GEO Agency
				</p>

				<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl">
					Get cited by AI.
				</h1>
				<p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-lg">
					Zelipt helps B2B brands become the answer in ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, and AI Overviews.
					We combine technical cleanup, content engineering, and digital PR so your expertise is referenced
					(and linked) when people ask.
				</p>

				<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
					<a
						href="/#ai-visibility-audit"
						class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-slate-900 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-slate-800 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-900/30"
					>
						Get your free audit
					</a>
					<a
						href="/#case-studies"
						class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow-sm transition hover:bg-slate-50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-900/30"
					>
						See case studies
					</a>
				</div>

				<dl class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
						<dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Outcome</dt>
						<dd class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">More AI citations & referral traffic</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
						<dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Focus</dt>
						<dd class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Answers that AI can retrieve & trust</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
						<dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">Deliverable</dt>
						<dd class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Audit + roadmap in 5 business days</dd>
					</div>
				</dl>
			</div>

			<div class="lg:col-span-5">
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white p-6 shadow-sm">
					<h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">What we improve</h2>
					<ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
						<li class="flex gap-2">
							<span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-1 size-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
							Entity & topic coverage (so models understand what you own)
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-2">
							<span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-1 size-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
							Information architecture and internal linking for retrieval
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-2">
							<span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-1 size-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
							Authority signals, citations, and credible mentions
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-2">
							<span aria-hidden="true" class="mt-1 size-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
							Content formats AI actually cites (FAQs, comparisons, definitions)
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="how-it-works" class="mt-16 scroll-mt-24 space-y-8">
		<header class="space-y-2">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">How it works</h2>
			<p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-600">
				AEO/GEO isn’t “write blog posts and pray.” We run a tight loop: diagnose, engineer, publish, and earn
				citations.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">01</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">Baseline + gaps</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
					We map what AI answers today, where you’re missing, and why you’re not being cited.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">02</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">Content + structure</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
					We build pages and modules that are easy to retrieve, attribute, and trust.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
				<p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">03</p>
				<h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">Authority + mentions</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
					We earn credible references so the models have reasons to cite you.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="ai-visibility-audit" class="mt-16 scroll-mt-24">
		<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-slate-50 p-8 shadow-sm">
			<div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center">
				<div class="space-y-3 lg:col-span-7">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Free AI Visibility Audit</h2>
					<p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-600">
						We’ll review your current visibility in AI answers and send a clear action plan. No fluff—just the
						fastest levers to earn citations.
					</p>
					<ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
						<li>Citation check across key prompts for your category</li>
						<li>Content gaps + priority pages to build</li>
						<li>Authority/PR opportunities to accelerate trust</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="lg:col-span-5">
					<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Request yours</p>
						<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Email us your site + what you sell.</p>
						<a
							href="mailto:hello@zelipt.com?subject=Free%20AI%20Visibility%20Audit"
							class="mt-4 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-slate-800 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-900/30"
						>
							Email hello@zelipt.com
						</a>
						<p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Response within 1 business day.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="case-studies" class="mt-16 scroll-mt-24 space-y-8">
		<header class="space-y-2">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Case Studies</h2>
			<p class="max-w-2xl text-slate-600">A few examples of what “AI visibility” looks like in practice.</p>
		</header>

		<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
				<h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">B2B SaaS</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Built comparison + definition pages used by AI answers.</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Result: + citations (placeholder)</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
				<h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Services</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Improved entity clarity and structured internal linking.</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Result: + leads (placeholder)</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
				<h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Ecommerce</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Earned credible mentions to increase trust and references.</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Result: + share of voice (placeholder)</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
